  <name>Length</name>
  <summary>Measure objects on screen</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GNOME application for measuring distances on screen to help you design and inspect layouts and graphics.
      Length includes the following features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pixels, centimeters, inches, or percentages as units</li>
      <li>Horizontal or vertical orientation</li>
      <li>Left-to-right or right-to-left orientation</li>
      <li>Transparency levels</li>
      <li>Track pointer position</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

